<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Página no encontrada — Lucky Lucky World</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body {
      font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
      background:#0D1B3E;
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
      text-align:center; padding:2rem;
    }
    .wrap { max-width:480px; }
    .num {
      font-size:8rem; font-weight:700;
      color:transparent;
      -webkit-text-stroke:3px #C9A84C;
      line-height:1; margin-bottom:1rem;
    }
    h1 { font-size:1.5rem; color:#fff; margin-bottom:0.8rem; }
    p { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size:0.92rem; margin-bottom:2rem; line-height:1.7; }
    a {
      display:inline-block;
      background:#C9A84C; color:#0D1B3E;
      padding:0.8rem 2rem; border-radius:8px;
      font-weight:600; font-size:0.9rem;
      text-decoration:none; transition:opacity 0.2s;
    }
    a:hover { opacity:0.85; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="num">404</div>
    <h1>Página no encontrada</h1>
    <p>La página que buscas no existe o fue movida.<br>Regresa al inicio y sigue participando.</p>
    <a href="/">← Volver al inicio</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>